Token.Abstract: Designated initializer. Initialize the process listener with an expected status and a block that will return status updates when called.

Parameter.Name: expectedStatus
Parameter.Abstract: The expected return status upon completion.

Parameter.Name: actualStatusBlock
Parameter.Abstract: The block that will return the actual status when called.

Parameter.Name: timeout
Parameter.Abstract: The amount of time before the asynchronous process is considered to time out.

Token.Abstract: Waits for the asynchronous process to complete.

ReturnValue.Abstract: The actual status at the time the process completes, or times out.
